@node P1InEqualQuad "P1: Equations and Inequalities - Quadratic Inequalities"
@{u}Solving Quadratic Inequalities@{uu}

There are two main methods of solving quadratic inequalities:

@{"Graph" link P1InEqualGraph}
@{"Table" link P1InEqualTable}
