@node M1Statics "M1: Statics"
@{u}Statics@{uu}

Statics is the study of objects at rest.  If a body is under the action of several forces we shall be choosing two perpendicular directions, finding the @{"components" link M1Comp} of each force in those directions and adding the forces together.

In statics the sum of the forces will be 0.
